  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to examine the long-term safety of Abatacept for the treatment
      of juvenile idiopathic arthritis (JIA) with particular in interest in the occurrence of
      serious infections, autoimmune disorders, and malignancies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
